sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Attendee
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Booking as Booking Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant MPesa as M-Pesa API
    participant Callback as Callback Handler
    participant DB as Database
    A ->> GW: POST /api/bookings
    GW ->> Booking: Create booking
    Booking ->> DB: Save booking (PENDING)
    Booking ->> Payment: Initiate payment
    Payment ->> Payment: Generate STK request
    Payment ->> MPesa: POST stkpush/v1/processrequest
    MPesa -->> A: STK Push prompt
    MPesa -->> Payment: Response with CheckoutRequestID
    A ->> A: Enter M-Pesa PIN
    MPesa ->> Callback: POST payment result
    Callback ->> Payment: Process callback
    Payment ->> DB: Update booking status
    Payment ->> Booking: Notify payment result
    Booking ->> DB: Generate tickets on success